    "Each model undergoes testing under various settings to assess the impact of these parameters on the effectiveness of both Syntax tree-based and LLM-based methods.",
    "To facilitate this evaluation, we employ the Syntax tree-based and LLM-based methods to generate 1,000 queries for each parameter setting.",
    "The ASR for different top-p values on LLMs is presented in Table 6.",
    "The results reveal that the effect of top-p on ASR differs among the LLMs tested, with each model exhibiting unique patterns of vulnerability.",
    "GPT 3.5 and Vicuna-13B show similar trends, with the highest ASR observed at a top-p value of 0.75 for both the Syntax Tree and LLM-based methods."
